com.demandware.appsec.secure.manipulation

Class AbstractManipulator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.demandware.appsec.secure.manipulation.AbstractManipulator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JavaScriptManipulator, JSONManipulator, URIManipulator, XMLManipulator

    public abstract class AbstractManipulator
extends Object
    Base implementation of a Manipulator (handles both filtering and encoding). Provides common functionality for character/string manipulations and bounds checking. Manipulators primarily implement "getCorrectCharacter" to determine any Character changes necessary based on Manipulator details.
    Author:
    Chris Smith
